<div style="background:#fff;"><div style="max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:8px 48px 44px;"><div style="margin-bottom:44px;"><div style="margin-bottom:26px;"><h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:28px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:0;">Why run Chip on Flex with Hana</h2></div><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:36px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:36px;">
      <div style="order:1;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--hana-blue);margin-bottom:10px;">Form factor freedom</div>
        <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:0 0 12px;text-wrap:balance;">Electronics that bend, fold and conform to the product</h3>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px;max-width:460px;">Putting the assembly on flex lets it wrap, fold or route around an enclosure where a rigid board won’t fit — common in compact optical, wearable and medical products.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;"><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:18px 1fr;gap:10px;align-items:baseline;padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.55;">Conforms to tight or curved enclosures</span></li><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:18px 1fr;gap:10px;align-items:baseline;padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.55;">Thinner and lighter than rigid + cable</span></li><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:18px 1fr;gap:10px;align-items:baseline;padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.55;">Suits optical, consumer and medical builds</span></li><li style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:18px 1fr;gap:10px;align-items:baseline;padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);"><span style="color:var(--hana-blue);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;">&rsaquo;</span><span style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:14px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.55;">SMT, wire bond and BGA all on one flex</span></li></ul>
      </div>
      <div style="order:2;"><div style="position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--surface);width:100%;height:320px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg,transparent 0 13px,rgba(18,131,221,0.06) 13px 14px);"><div style="position:absolute;top:10px;left:12px;width:18px;height:18px;opacity:.4;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--hana-blue)" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle><path d="M12 3v4M12 17v4M3 12h4M17 12h4"></path></svg></div><span style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--ink-3);text-align:center;padding:0 18px;line-height:1.5;">[ Chip-on-flex line in operation ]</span></div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:36px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:36px;">
      <div style="order:2;">
        <div style="font-family:var(--font-text);font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--hana-blue);margin-bottom:10px;">EMS + OSAT, vertically integrated</div>
